            <abstract id="ref2" label="Abstract">Burton White was a stage manager, consultant, and producer for several different Pittsburgh theatre production companies in the 1980's. These papers reflect the early professional career of Burton White and consist of production books and notes, mostly from productions in the Pittsburgh area.</abstract>
